==Noun==
#A [[statement]] attributed to [[someone]] else.
#A [[quotation mark]].
#A summary of work to be done with a set price.
#A [[quotation]].

''In technically correct English, "quote" is not a noun at all.  For meanings 1,3,4 above use "quotation"; for 2 use "quotation mark".  Quote is commonly used in almost all circles, however.''

